_olex2_refinement_description    
;
1. Fixed Uiso
 At 1.2 times of:
  All N(H,H) groups
2. Uiso/Uaniso restraints and constraints
Uanis(N1) = Uanis(N2) = Uanis(N3) = Uanis(N4)
3. Rigid body (RIGU) restrains
 N1, C1, N2, N3, C2, N4
 with sigma for 1-2 distances of 0.002 and sigma for 1-3 distances of 0.002
4. Others
 Fixed Sof: H3A(0.5) H3B(0.5) H2A(0.5) H2B(0.5)
5.a X=CH2 refined with riding coordinates:
 N3(H3A,H3B), N4(H4A,H4B), N2(H2A,H2B), N1(H1A,H1B)
;
